::DevilDuer::

The bushes near Hot Rod rustle, and DevilDuer steps out. He was on his way 
back to the Alliance base, and accidently came across Hot Rod's path.

"Maximal," he growls, immediately lowering into a fighting crouch and 
punching at Hot Rod.
